  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Tuition Teacher (Science & Biology Subject)</strong></li><li><strong>Basic Salary: $3,500 - $4,500</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours : 3 Weekdays 1.00pm-8.00pm & 2 Weekends 10.00am-7.00pm</strong></li><li><strong>2 Off Days on Weekdays</strong></li><li><strong>Location:   Alexandra Village [ Between Telok Blangah / Queenstown ]</strong></li><li><strong>Required Graduate / NIE-Trained Tutor</strong></li><li><strong>Teach  Lower Secondary Science and Upper Secondary Biology</strong></li><li><strong>Class Group: 6 Pax max</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Teaching students Science & Biology subject according to the MOE syllabus and curriculum</li><li>Guiding and motivating students to succeed in their academics</li><li>Curriculum development when necessary</li><li>Monitoring of student work</li><li>Following up with and updating parents on their child’s progress</li></ul><p><br />#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p></p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p><p></p>",
